parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants are not provided with the necessary protection to mitigate the impact of the crash.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries or fatalities to the occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadvertent deployment of airbags can cause unexpected and sudden movements, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unexpectedly
without any apparent reason or crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which if not addressed, can lead to airbag failure to deploy in a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause distraction, injury, and accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The sunroof explodes or shatters spontaneously
making a loud noise
and causing glass to fall into the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
grinding noise when shifting gears
and the vehicle goes into reverse unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause inconvenience and compromise the security of the vehicle.
symptoms: The door lock actuator fails
causing the door to lock or unlock unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: Liquid leaks under the passenger's seat
causing a horrible stench in the car
and debris gets clogged in the air conditioning ventilation system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield and glass can cause distraction, injury, and accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The windshield laminated glass separates
causing pieces of glass to fall into the driver's lap
and the sunroof explodes or shatters spontaneously.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view mirror can cause distraction and compromise the safety of the vehicle.
symptoms: The auto-dimming rear view mirror does not dim properly
causing glare from rear cars with headlights on
and the body of the side rear view mirrors blocks a significant area of the driver's view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine and performance can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates on acceleration
feels as though the engine is dying
and has happened multiple times on streets
highways
turning
and going straight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without pressing the gas pedal
the vehicle accelerates while braking
the vehicle hesitates to accelerate
the vehicle jerks or bucks while slowing down or decelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down in time.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle accelerates while braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is unable to shift gears smoothly or loses power.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to accelerate
the vehicle jerks or bucks while shifting gears
the vehicle loses power while driving
the cruise control does not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cruise control issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is unable to maintain a steady speed or accelerate unexpectedly.
symptoms: The cruise control does not function properly
the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly while using cruise control
the vehicle loses power while using cruise control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut down, leading to a loss of power steering, lights, and other essential systems, which can be dangerous and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system shuts down
no power to any electrical systems
lights flicker
all dash lights come on
the vehicle won't start
and the battery and alternator need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The infotainment system is stuck in reboot mode
the rearview camera fails to turn on intermittently
and the rearview camera image is intermittently blurry.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, especially if the brakes fail to engage or the vehicle vibrates abnormally while driving.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates abnormally while driving
the brake system is not operating as designed
and the brake pedal sticks to the floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls after getting a full tank of gas
the gas pedal sticks to the floor
and the fuel pump acts up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to unlock or lock unexpectedly, which can be a safety hazard, especially if the doors unlock while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The door lock actuator fails to lock or unlock
the doors unlock or lock unexpectedly
and the doors may not lock or unlock with the key fob.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the battery to drain, leading to the vehicle stalling or not starting.
symptoms: The battery is completely drained
the alternator is not charging the battery
and the vehicle won't start.
